                "invention-title": [
                    "Quick-response total organic carbon on-line monitoring system",
                    "一种快速响应总有机碳在线监测系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a quick-response total organic carbon on-line monitoring system which comprises a sampling device, an analyzer, an air compressor, a hydrogen-air all-in-one machine and a tail gas exhaust pipe. A sampling probe is arranged in the sampling device, and the sampling device is used for collecting sample gas in a pollution source flue; a first proportional valve pressure sensor and a first air resistor are arranged between an outlet pipeline of the detector and the injection pump; the first proportional valve pressure sensor is communicated with the outside atmosphere; and the other end of the first air resistor is connected to a pipeline between the detector and the second proportional valve pressure sensor. The injection pump is communicated with the air inlet pipeline and the air outlet pipeline of the detector, constant negative pressure sampling is generated after instrument air is supplied by the air compressor and passes through the injection pump, and the response time of online monitoring of the total organic carbon can be shortened by adopting the pressure sensor and automatically adjusting the negative pressure value of the pipeline; the system has the advantages of fast response, low cost and high stability, and has a good application prospect."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种快速响应总有机碳在线监测系统，包括采样装置、分析仪、空压机、氢空一体机和尾气排放管；采样装置，其内置采样探头，用于采集污染源烟道中的样气；检测器的出口管路与喷射泵之间设置有第一比例阀压力传感器和第一气阻；第一比例阀压力传感器与外界大气连通；第一气阻的另一端连接在检测器与第二比例阀压力传感器之间的管路上。本发明通过喷射泵与检测器进气口管路和出气口管路连通，依靠空压机供应仪表风通过喷射泵后产生恒定负压采样，采用压力传感器和自动调节管路负压值，可以减少总有机碳在线监测的响应时间；本系统以响应快、成本低、高稳定性的优势具有很好的应用前景。"
                }
            ]
